> > 6.  New terrain based defense skills:
> 
> The overall idea is OK, I'm not so sure about the maximum added
> defense being 100. At the least you should not let people use XXXX 4
> times a month for the entire game, as that goes against the limits
> you've placed on STUDY, etc. Perhaps a limit of 35 would be
> appropriate, that's as good as a minimum castle.
> 
> > Beastmastery
> 
> I would urge another adjustment of breeding rates: make it inversely
> proportional to the combat power of the beast. Even with the 1 worker
> requirement, breeding dragons at the curent rate is too good. Even
> getting only one dragon per month per breeder is also too good.
> 
> Dragons should weigh more. Other beasts too.
> 
